FBIS4-31212 "dreeu109_m_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 THE FORMER YUGOSLAV REPUBLIC OF MACEDONIA Albanian-Montenegrin Border Crossing Closed Albanian-Montenegrin Border Crossing Closed AU0606133594 Skopje MILS-NEWS in English 6 Jun 94 AU0606133594 Skopje MILS-NEWS English BFN [Unattributed report: "Albanian-Montenegro Border Closed"] [Text] The only official border-crossing between Montenegro and Albania, near Bozaj, 20km away from Podgorica, was closed two days ago. Unofficial sources explain this with authorities' attempts to stop the massive oil smuggling from Albania into Montenegro.
